# Blog Images Directory

This directory contains all images used in blog posts.

## Structure:
- Featured images for post headers
- Inline images for content sections
- Infographics and diagrams

## Naming Convention:
- Descriptive filenames with keywords
- Format: {topic}-{description}.jpg/webp
- Example: visa-rejection-appeal-documents.jpg

## Optimization:
- All images should be < 200KB
- WebP format preferred
- Responsive sizing configured
